{"data": [{"id": "4741820", "title": "Copa Holdings: The Most Undervalued Airline Stock To Buy", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"COPA Airlines Boeing 737 MAX 9\" data-id=\"1928902966\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1021px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1928902966/image_1928902966.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Angel Di Bilio</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Airlines do not make for the most stable investments. The reward can be high, but that's mostly the take when you ride the waves rather than holding the stock through upward and downward movements of the stock price. Copa Holdings S.A. (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/192890