r-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LND\" title=\"BrasilAgro - Companhia Brasileira de Propriedades Agr\u00edcolas\">LND</a></span>) reported 1Q25 results, with an improvement in the margin of core crops (mainly soybeans from inventory carry and sugarcane from an improvement in prices). The company also completed the sale of one of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1502913963/image_1502913963.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741827-brasilagro-is-cheaper-after-q1-but-still-not-an-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 22:03:15"}, {"id": "4741849", "title": "OPEC+ Meeting In Focus: Will Oil Production Cuts Continue Through March 2025?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Golden Oil Bubbles\" data-id=\"1170674069\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1150px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jonathan Knowles</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em></p> <p>Oil prices are holding steady near the $72.35 support level, staying in a 6-day period of little movement. OPEC+ meets on Thursday, and there\u2019s a higher chance they will extend their oil output cuts to Q1 2025.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1170674069/image_1170674069.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741849-opec-plus-meeting-in-focus-will-oil-production-cuts-continue-through-march-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:56:00"}, {"id": "4741816", "title": "The Children's Place: The Turnaround Hiccup", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business on Wall Street in Manhattan\" data-id=\"1220627489\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6240px\" height=\"4160px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Pgiam/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>The Children's Place, Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PLCE\" title=\"The Children's Place, Inc.\">PLCE</a></span>) is a retailer that has been in an extremely volatile trade. We called for a rapid-return buy at $9 in September. The stock more than doubled in a few sessions. However, the stock has</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1220627489/image_1220627489.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741816-the-childrens-place-the-turnaround-hiccup", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:41:25"}, {"id": "4741815", "title": "Property Type Round-Up From REITworld 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone Shot of Las Vegas Strip at Nightfall\" data-id=\"1808874665\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1808874665/image_1808874665.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">halbergman</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We recently attended the annual REITWorld conference, where we conducted 33 meetings with REIT CEOs and CFOs. We also attended two organized dinners, three property tours, and a run around the Las Vegas strip with a REIT management team to maximize our</p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741815-property-type-round-up-from-reitworld-2024", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:41:01"}, {"id": "4741814", "title": "AMD: Positioned For Takeoff As 2025 Demand Gains Momentum", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Abstract circuit board with a lot of micro chips\" data-id=\"1397047849\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sankai</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The recent pullback in <b>Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AMD\" title=\"Advanced Micro Devices, Inc.\">AMD</a></span>) stock following its <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4220849-advanced-micro-devices-non-gaap-eps-of-0_92-in-line-revenue-of-6_82m-misses-6_7b\">Q3 2024 earnings report</a> presents what, I believe, is a Dip-Buy opportunity for long-term investors. Because of AMD's accelerating momentum in the artificial intelligence and data</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397047849/image_1397047849.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741814-amd-positioned-for-takeoff-as-2025-demand-gains-momentum", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:32:32"}, {"id": "4741837", "title": "Singapore Banks Expect Wealth Management, Loans To Drive Earnings Momentum", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Singapore flag waving in the wind against background of peoples park old building\" data-id=\"1263355177\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5000px\" height=\"3333px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kandl</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Singapore's three largest banks expect wealth management and growing loan portfolios to drive earnings in 2025 after they posted strong earnings growth in the third quarter.</p> <p>DBS Group Holdings Ltd. (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DBSDF\" title=\"DBS Group Holdings Ltd\">OTCPK:DBSDF</a>) reported net income of S$3.03 billion</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1263355177/image_1263355177.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741837-singapore-banks-expect-wealth-management-loans-to-drive-earnings-momentum", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:28:00"}, {"id": "4741809", "title": "EVgo: Q3 Results Likely To Support Reversal Rally", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young Asian woman uses her smartphone to make contactless payment after charging her car at an electric vehicle (&lt;a href='https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EV' title=''&gt;EV&lt;/a&gt;) charging station\" data-id=\"2159031349\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Images By Tang Ming Tung/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Initiating Coverage</h2> <p>I am initiating coverage on <strong>EVgo, Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/EVGO\" title=\"EVgo, Inc.\">EVGO</a></span>) with a \"<em>Buy</em>\" rating and an investment horizon of 24 months. I believe that EVgo is among the best</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159031349/image_2159031349.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741809-evgo-stock-q3-results-likely-to-support-reversal-rally", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:14:53"}, {"id": "4741829", "title": "Australian Banks Rely On Capital To Offset Margin Pressures, Profit Declines", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Random little white piggy banks\" data-id=\"1072593766\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5174px\" height=\"3454px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Australia's biggest banks demonstrated resilience in their financial results for the recently concluded fiscal year, reflecting robust capital levels amid intense competition.</p> <p>The country's four major lenders reported a decline in their net profits for the fiscal</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593766/image_1072593766.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741829-australian-banks-rely-on-capital-offset-margin-pressures-profit-declines", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:09:00"}, {"id": "4741830", "title": "UBS Global Industrials and Transportation Conference", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Stanley Black &amp; Decker, Inc. in conjunction with this event.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106009\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741830-ubs-global-industrials-and-transportation-conference", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 21:05:18"}]}